{"title":"Accessories","description":"Hario gives you the tools to go beyond brewing and grinding with these essential coffee accessories.","products":[{"product_id":"hario-3oz-shot-glass","title":"Hario 3oz Shot Glass","description":"Perfect for measuring out shots on your espresso machine. Made from high quality Hario heat-resistant glass, and marked lines to 2oz. 80ml capacity.","brand":"Hario Canada","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":5430998339,"sku":"SGS-80","price":8.0,"currency_code":"CAD","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0942\/1790\/products\/hario_shot_glass.jpg?v=1438288845"},{"product_id":"hario-15oz-glass","title":"Hario 15oz Glass","description":"This is the ultimate glasswear for hot drinks. For a medium cup of coffee or tea, this lightweight double-walled glass will keep your drink hot, while staying cool on the outside. Not only that, it's also designed to integrate with the Hario V60 range - meaning you can put a V60 pourover straight on top, and pour straight into the glass. It also works beautifully with the Hario Largo for tea. The beehive design fits in with the rest of the Hario Beehive range, and makes it really easy to hold.","brand":"Hario","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":5431004739,"sku":"VCG-15","price":22.0,"currency_code":"CAD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0942\/1790\/products\/hario_15oz_glass.jpg?v=1438258781"},{"product_id":"hario-5oz-glass","title":"Hario 5oz Glass","description":"High quality Hario heat-resistant glass in a 5oz size. Made in Japan. 140ml capacity.","brand":"Hario Canada","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":5431013059,"sku":"SGS-140","price":10.2,"currency_code":"CAD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0942\/1790\/products\/hario_5oz_glass.jpg?v=1438258790"},{"product_id":"hario-copper-kettle","title":"Hario Copper Kettle","description":"\u003cp\u003eThis kettle is just so perfectly... well, kettle. With some key improvements to the iconic Buono kettle such as adjusting the spout, widening the base, and increasing pouring precision. This beauty has excellent thermal conductivity, and the copper makes it anti-bacterial. Full copper body, with a brass handle, natural wood lid knob, and nickel plated interior. And a great value addition to any coffee making collection.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMaterials: Copper body with nickel plated interior, brass handle, natural wood lid holder\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCompatible with direct flame heating surfaces\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFunctional Capacity: 700ml\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eMade in Japan\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"Hario Canada","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":5431021891,"sku":"VKBN-90CP","price":185.0,"currency_code":"CAD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0942\/1790\/products\/hario_copper_kettle.jpg?v=1438258810"},{"product_id":"hario-paper-stand-white","title":"Hario Paper Stand White","description":"The Hario Paper Filter Display Stand is made from the same thick, quality porcelain ceramic as the V60 brewer. Holds up to 100 paper filters in either V60-01 or V60-02 sizes.","brand":"Hario Canada","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":5431052611,"sku":"VPS-100W","price":21.0,"currency_code":"CAD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0942\/1790\/products\/hario_paper_stand.jpg?v=1438290840"},{"product_id":"hario-bamboo-stirrer","title":"Hario Bamboo Stirrer","description":"Soft, efficient, a good length for any brew method, and paddle shaped to give a more even agitation. It's also really easy to keep clean as all it requires is a wipe down with a damp cloth after use, then left to dry.","brand":"Hario Canada","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":5431060611,"sku":"BA-15","price":6.0,"currency_code":"CAD","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0942\/1790\/products\/hario_bamboo.jpg?v=1438289958"},{"product_id":"hario-buono-kettle-small","title":"Hario Buono Kettle 1.0L","description":"\u003cp\u003eThe Hario Buono kettle is pretty much the standard in pouring kettles for home or cafe use. It allows you to direct the flow of the water over your coffee bed and also control the pace, ensuring you have the potential to get the most out of your coffee.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThis kettle is also burner-friendly, so if the feeling takes you, you can bring it to the boil like old fashioned kettles. Just don't try and heat it in the microwave. This is the small (1L to the Rim) version of the standard Hario Buono kettle.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cmeta charset=\"utf-8\"\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStainless Steel\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCompatible with induction and direct flame heating surfaces\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eFunctional Capacity: 600ml\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e","brand":"Hario Canada","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":5431091523,"sku":"VKB-100HSV","price":67.0,"currency_code":"CAD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0942\/1790\/products\/hario_buono_small_66d851fb-f7be-4bfc-b9e3-661b51e6cdbe.jpg?v=1438258922"},{"product_id":"hario-glass-canister-1l","title":"Hario Glass Canister 1L","description":"It's essential to keep tasty coffee beans sealed in an airtight container to keep them fresh and prevent flavour alteration over time. Our Japanese Glass friends at Hario have created this simple one litre sealed glass container specifically for keeping your stash of beans tasting their best.","brand":"Hario Canada","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":5431104259,"sku":"MCN-300B","price":15.0,"currency_code":"CAD","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0942\/1790\/products\/hario_canister.jpg?v=1438258943"},{"product_id":